These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, march
2 different pets are kept: snake, frog
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Birthday   | may  | march |
| Pet     | frog | snake  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: country, trance
There are 2 different favourite colors: pink, purple
1. the fan of trance is on the right of the person who likes pink##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Music-Genre    | country      | trance         |
| Color   | pink | purple |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: writing, chess
There are 2 different nationalities: nigerian, thai
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Hobby   | chess | writing   |
| Nationality       | thai  | nigerian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
City: colone, venice
The people have 2 different jobs:  pilot, freelancer
1. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the pilot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| City   | colone  | venice |
| Job         | pilot | freelancer    |

